{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_88","type":"agent_message","text":"Implemented the M14 shell on top of the existing dashboard-session contract and planner.\n\nThe main changes are in [dashboard_app_shell.py](/home/jack/Documents/github/personal/fly_neural_simulation/flywire_wave_repo/src/flywire_wave/dashboard_app_shell.py#L38), which now writes a deterministic offline app shell with a five-pane layout, embedded bootstrap payload, content-hashed CSS/JS assets, and one linked client state model for `selected_arm_pair`, `selected_neuron_id`, `selected_readout_id`, `active_overlay_id`, `comparison_mode`, and `time_cursor`. [dashboard_session_planning.py](/home/jack/Documents/github/personal/fly_neural_simulation/flywire_wave_repo/src/flywire_wave/dashboard_session_planning.py#L474) now packages those app assets and returns their paths. The static frontend lives in [dashboard_shell.css](/home/jack/Documents/github/personal/fly_neural_simulation/flywire_wave_repo/src/flywire_wave/dashboard_assets/dashboard_shell.css) and [dashboard_shell.js](/home/jack/Documents/github/personal/fly_neural_simulation/flywire_wave_repo/src/flywire_wave/dashboard_assets/dashboard_shell.js), and the new CLI wrapper is [29_dashboard_shell.py](/home/jack/Documents/github/personal/fly_neural_simulation/flywire_wave_repo/scripts/29_dashboard_shell.py#L28). I also added `make` targets in [Makefile](/home/jack/Documents/github/personal/fly_neural_simulation/flywire_wave_repo/Makefile#L108), package-data registration in [pyproject.toml](/home/jack/Documents/github/personal/fly_neural_simulation/flywire_wave_repo/pyproject.toml#L19), a shell smoke test in [test_dashboard_app_shell.py](/home/jack/Documents/github/personal/fly_neural_simulation/flywire_wave_repo/tests/test_dashboard_app_shell.py#L35), and the required rationale note at [FW-M14-003_rationale.md](/home/jack/Documents/github/personal/fly_neural_simulation/flywire_wave_repo/docs/ui_dashboard_notes/FW-M14-003_rationale.md#L1).\n\nDocumented local entrypoint: `make dashboard-open CONFIG=<path-to-config.yaml>` or `python3 scripts/29_dashboard_shell.py build --config <path-to-config.yaml> --manifest manifests/examples/milestone_1_demo.yaml --schema schemas/milestone_1_experiment_manifest.schema.json --design-lock config/milestone_1_design_lock.yaml --open`.\n\nVerified:\n- `make test` passed: 202 tests, OK\n- `python3 -m unittest tests.test_dashboard_session_planning tests.test_dashboard_app_shell -v` passed after the final shell tweak\n- Direct CLI fixture check succeeded: `scripts/29_dashboard_shell.py build ...` produced deterministic `app/index.html` and `app/dashboard_asset_manifest.json` from packaged local artifacts without live FlyWire access"}}
